# Hashed denylist (sha256 of lowercased private tokens). A SECONDARY tripwire;
# the primary privacy guarantee is provenance (every artifact derives from the
# synthetic corpus). Plaintext tokens are NOT stored here by design — guarding a
# name must not publish it. denylist_scan.py hashes candidate tokens from the
# corpus + committed JSON and checks membership. Regenerate from the private
# token list (kept outside this repo) when it changes.
